#define R(p,a,r) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(r))+sin(r)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    O=vec4(0);
    vec3 p,r=iResolution,d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1.));
    for(float i=0.,e,g=0.,t=iTime;
        i++<80.;
        O.xyz+=mix(vec3(1),H(p.x+p.z),.6)*.01/exp(.3*i*i*e)
    ){
        p=d*g,
        p.z-=1.5,
        p=R(p,normalize(H(t*.03)-.5),t*.3)-i/1e4;
        for(int i=0;i++<3;)
            p=abs(p),
            p=p.y<p.x?p.zxy:p.zyx;
        g+=e=abs(p.y)-.5-.01*smoothstep(.3,.0,abs(length(asin(cos(p.xz*25.)))-1.)-.3);
    }
}
